  "text": "Another G1/S-regulator that might play a role in the proper Development 131 (13) Research article mitotic-to-endocycle transition in follicle cells is Cyclin E [CITATION_1] . Drosophila Cyclin E forms a complex with the DmCdc2c/Cdk2 kinase and controls the progression through the S phase; its downregulation limits embryonic proliferation and its oscillation is required for endocycling [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
